- needs OpenCV 2.1.0 -- http://sourceforge.net/projects/opencvlibrary/
- packages needed before OpenCV compile:
libgtk2.0-dev libunicap2-dev libucil2-dev libswscale-dev libdc1394-22-dev libv4l-dev libxine-dev libavformat-dev libglut3-dev libwxgtk2.8-dev
- needs export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/usr/local/lib
